author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Jiangsu Changbao Steeltube To Set Up Units, Unit To Invest In Fund
text:
April 19 (Reuters) - Jiangsu Changbao Steeltube Co Ltd :
* SAYS IT PLANS TO SET UP UNIT WITH REGISTERED CAPITAL OF 500 MILLION YUAN ($79.67 million)
* SAYS UNIT PLANS TO INVEST 510 MILLION YUAN TO SET UP HEALTHCARE INVESTMENT FUND WITH PARTNERS
* SAYS IT PLANS TO SET UP MEDICAL MANAGEMENT UNIT IN SHANGHAI WITH REGISTERED CAPITAL OF ABOUT 100 MILLION YUAN Source text in Chinese: bit.ly/2HMF8Ie ; bit.ly/2J8ljdC ; bit.ly/2J9ro9M Further company coverage: ($1 = 6.2755 Chinese yuan renminbi) (Reporting by Hong Kong newsroom)
